  "local_port": 59426,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What online stores accept food stamps for delivery in FL?",
  "response": "In Florida, **SNAP (Supplemental Nutrition Assistance Program)** benefits, commonly known as food stamps, can be used for online grocery purchases. The USDA has partnered with several retailers to allow SNAP participants to shop online for groceries. Here are some online stores that accept SNAP/EBT for delivery in Florida:\n\n1. **Amazon**  \n   - Amazon accepts SNAP/EBT for eligible food items through its Amazon Fresh and Amazon Pantry services.  \n   - Website: [www.amazon.com](https://www.amazon.com)\n\n2. **Walmart**  \n   - Walmart allows SNAP/EBT for online grocery orders, including delivery and pickup.  \n   - Website: [www.walmart.com](https://www.walmart.com)\n\n3. **ALDI**  \n   - ALDI accepts SNAP/EBT for online grocery orders via Instacart.  \n   - Website: [www.aldi.us](https://www.aldi.us)\n\n4. **Publix**  \n   - Publix accepts SNAP/EBT for online grocery orders through Instacart.  \n   - Website: [www.publix.com](https://www.publix.com)\n\n5. **BJ's Wholesale Club**  \n   - BJ's accepts SNAP/EBT for online grocery orders via Instacart.  \n   - Website: [www.bjs.com](https://www.bjs.com)\n\n6. **Food Lion**  \n   - Food Lion accepts SNAP/EBT for online orders through Instacart.  \n   - Website: [www.foodlion.com](https://www.foodlion.com)\n\n7. **Target**  \n   - Target accepts SNAP/EBT for eligible grocery items online, either for pickup or delivery via Shipt.  \n   - Website: [www.target.com](https://www.target.com)\n\n### How to Use SNAP Online:  \n- Check the retailer\u2019s website for SNAP/EBT payment options at checkout.  \n- You may need to link your EBT card to your account on the retailer\u2019s platform.  \n- Note that delivery fees or tips are **not** covered by SNAP and must be paid separately using another payment method.\n\nFor the most up-to-date information, visit the **USDA SNAP Online Purchasing Pilot page**: [USDA SNAP Online](https://www.fns.usda.gov/snap/online-purchasing-pilot).",
  "temperature": 1.0,
